    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3; this gap is accepted because the ASTM F1717 standard condition is the sole regulatory submission basis and the model is not applied outside this validated regime. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval) for all three QoIs fall below the 1.96 acceptance threshold. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the medium-risk COU. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been affixed to this package.",
